name: FISHING FIASCO 🐠🐟🐙
description:
Fishing Fiasco 🐠🐟🐙 is a fun filled addictive fishing game which is great for everyone.

It is free, easy and very simple to play, improve your skills every time you level up as the fishes become faster.

Try to capture as many fishes as you can by casting your fishing line from your boat ⛵🐟

Test your Speed and skills by playing this wonderful game today.

You will be literally hooked 🎣😉
